  <brief_title>The Use of Reminders in Implementing an E-learning Program in General Practice</brief_title>
  <official_title>Implementation of an E-learning Program in Diagnostic Evaluation of Dementia by Reminders: A RCT Among General Practitioners in Copenhagen</official_title>
